For example, large studies on the effects of the 4th dose are already rolling out in Israel.
And according to these studies, in most patients there is a fivefold increase in antibodies, which already has the long-term effect mentioned by you.
Just like any other vaccination, it will have its own vaccination schedule, but it is too early for that.
